text: Francisco Viacava (born 22 March 1961) is a Peruvian rower. He competed in the men's coxed pair event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Peruvian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Peru Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Pan American Games medalists in rowing Category:Pan American Games bronze medalists for Peru Category:Rowers at the 1983 Pan American Games
